@BaseUrl = {{$dotenv BASE_URL}}/documents

### Test endpoint
GET {{BaseUrl}}/test

### Upload files
POST {{BaseUrl}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="olympic_building_information.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< test_files/olympic_building_information.txt
