### Get List of Documents
GET {{BaseUrl}}

@documentid = 71281334-5074-40f7-8b57-af0c25f204f3

### Get Information for a document
GET {{BaseUrl}}/{{documentid}}

### Delete a document
DELETE {{BaseUrl}}/{{documentid}}
